      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've been reading online that taking strong meds for no reason is actually bad for your gut microbiome and can cause other issues. if the actual infection is gone, isn't it basically just putting extra stress on my body for no reason? i'd much rather just stop now while i'm ahead than risk side effects from the rest of the week.",
