      "content": "i just don't feel like the \"minimal\" risk is worth it for another 7 days when i'm clearly not sick anymore. if i just stop now and it happens to come back, i can just go back to the doctor then. isn't it more logical to just stop once the symptoms are gone so i'm not flooding my system with stuff i don't need? feels like the safest way to avoid unnecessary side effects.",
